{"tid":1763556,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"美國國會大廈天花的濕壁畫—「戰爭、科學、海洋、商業、機械、農業」","createTime":"2019-11-30T12:28:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T07:22:40.000Z","uid":14918,"like":46,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"df7ac141d8318c7aacaaad82b73621fc5b97a464","tid":1763556,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:28:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/86/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_War.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F86%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_War.jpg&h=e00c067e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n戰爭 <br />\n位於華盛頓正下方的是「自由」即哥倫比亞，為戰爭的擬人化象徵。此場景描述一位女士舉劍為自由而戰；她身穿披肩，頭戴頭盔，手持以美國國旗為主色調的盾牌，漫步在代表僭主與君王權力的人群圖像之上。在「自由」左邊協助她的是一隻兇猛的白頭海雕（也就是美國國鳥），爪子抓着箭矢與雷光之箭（英語：Thunderbolt）（與美國國徽中老鷹抓起箭矢的形象相連結）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/b/b4/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_Science.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Fb%2Fb4%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_Science.jpg&h=1faeb209&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n科學 <br />\n羅馬戰爭與智慧女神彌涅耳瓦，身戴頭盔，手持長矛，指著一臺發電機。而發電機旁則是儲存電力的電池。彌涅耳瓦後方則是寫作臺。這幅畫像象徵偉大的美國發明物。美國的科學家與發明家富蘭克林、薩繆爾&middot;摩斯、羅伯特&middot;富爾頓則看着彌涅耳瓦。畫面左側，一名教師示範如何使用兩腳規。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/f/fd/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_Marine.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2Ff%2Ffd%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_Marine.jpg&h=322532dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n海洋 <br />\n此畫像中，羅馬海神涅普頓，手持三叉戟，頭戴海草王冠，駕着由海馬拖拉的貝殼戰車。自海而生的愛神維納斯，正協助鋪設連結美國與愛爾蘭的跨大西洋電報線，背景則是一艘裝有煙囪的蒸汽船。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/8/84/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_Commerce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F8%2F84%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_Commerce.jpg&h=04a7ac91&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n商業 <br />\n羅馬的商業之神墨丘利，頭戴有翼帽，腳穿涼鞋，手持雙蛇杖，正給與一袋黃金給美國獨立戰爭的開國元勳金融家羅伯特&middot;莫里斯。畫面左側， 一群男人搬運推車上的箱子；畫面右側，船員與錨引領走向「海洋」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/49/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_Mechanics.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F4%2F49%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_Mechanics.jpg&h=68d5823a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n機械 <br />\n此場景描繪羅馬火神與鐵匠之神兀兒肯站在鐵砧旁邊，腳上踩着加農砲，加農砲旁邊有一堆砲彈；背景則是蒸氣機。在熔爐旁邊的人則是要代表國會大廈圓頂工程的煉鐵主管查爾斯&middot;湯瑪斯。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/2/21/Flickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%2C_Agriculture.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F2%2F21%2FFlickr_-_USCapitol_-_Apotheosis_of_Washington%252C_Agriculture.jpg&h=38dfe50c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n農業 <br />\n羅馬的農業女神刻瑞斯， 頭戴一捆麥穗，手執象徵豐收的豐裕之角，坐在麥考密克的機械收割機上。年輕美國的擬人化男子，頭戴佛里幾亞無邊便帽，牽着馬的韁繩。而花神佛洛拉則在地上收集花朵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n此圓頂完成於1863年，布魯米迪接着在美國內戰結束後的11個月內完成此作品；他則因為此濕壁畫獲得40,000美元（現今約為625,826美元）的酬勞。"},{"pid":"c75d25a4251340d23f2a204809e75c40909d7586","tid":1763556,"uid":38164,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:47:56.000Z","msg":"大國基礎"},{"pid":"a0558f8574a6422b513513b2bdfd7de27be13c70","tid":1763556,"uid":7102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T12:48:23.000Z","msg":"請手動廣傳<br />\n<br />\n121尖沙咀大遊行<br />\n已經獲發不反對通知書<br />\n日期：12月1日<br />\n集合時間：下午三點<br />\n集合地點：尖沙咀鐘樓<br />\n終點：紅磡體育館<br />\n遊行終結時間：下午六點"},{"pid":"48235b49ca6997bcfc2add3448ab8d427f7dbb50","tid":1763556,"uid":14918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T13:53:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df59db0493e6e11ed0a1cad2eac0f7646e2c07be","tid":1763556,"uid":71133,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"支那去到今日都未有咁嘅眼光，俾呢d國家做到一流大國簡直係人類文明嘅恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae6b5d659402f2a206b170c1df9487cc97ce53a2","tid":1763556,"uid":130488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:31:56.000Z","msg":"好靚<br />\n第一次聽"},{"pid":"cf8abd31e8c0a9d7d84d1a7a2e4350d7a41e9c8a","tid":1763556,"uid":229275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:43:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6fcc54d2fc44d446f4daec7e3ac2c1951051cf92","tid":1763556,"uid":191366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:46:13.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"6087bc86e9ac544a691e3a6963ffb4c1a95e352e","tid":1763556,"uid":75664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:52:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edadbbd416396baa1cc9a21a45190f3f3cc40f78","tid":1763556,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"df59db0493e6e11ed0a1cad2eac0f7646e2c07be","tid":1763556,"uid":71133,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"支那去到今日都未有咁嘅眼光，俾呢d國家做到一流大國簡直係人類文明嘅恥辱<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:16:30.000Z","msg":"因為美國以己度人 以為支那會發財立品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a72d811f934802bd07f10a4d849a1821f2f7a2","tid":1763556,"uid":199957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:16:59.000Z","msg":"6樣野入面 支那好似樣樣都唔掂"},{"pid":"3833b4da09ddd7ccc384db237e86bddd2cb17ba3","tid":1763556,"uid":290006,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"正，香港人有幸受到西方文化影響，先至識得欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西方追求真理，信念堅定，成就科學，亦都從小就識得每個人都服膺於真理/上帝之下<br />\n<br />\n支那追求和諧，於人前（尤其於長輩前）虛偽度日，以奉承權貴為尚，逆長輩意就被視為異類，到自己做咗長輩終於唔使服從就變得唯我獨尊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1327554a3848118b2e5e8dbf854fb09b5d0067","tid":1763556,"uid":291065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:45:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3bbd659e466c68664499be989d8d171e3d674dd","tid":1763556,"uid":51625,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3833b4da09ddd7ccc384db237e86bddd2cb17ba3","tid":1763556,"uid":290006,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T15:43:45.000Z","msg":"正，香港人有幸受到西方文化影響，先至識得欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n西方追求真理，信念堅定，成就科學，亦都從小就識得每個人都服膺於真理/上帝之下<br />\n<br />\n支那追求和諧，於人前（尤其於長輩前）虛偽度日，以奉承權貴為尚，逆長輩意就被視為異類，到自己做咗長輩終於唔使服從就變得唯我獨尊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-02T19:19:27.000Z","msg":"其實仲有一樣香港人係未俾西方影響到。<br />\n<br />\n就係如何看待生命。<br />\n<br />\n人之所以有價值，值得被愛同埋被尊重，並唔係因為佢嘅地位、身份、外貌、擁有嘅嘢、做到嘅嘢。純粹係因為佢係一個人。<br />\n<br />\n而呢樣嘢正正係西方文明社會嘅核心價值之一，亦係一個現代文明社會嘅基礎。"},{"pid":"5d460a3c2a0d83890ffdeff1a2d75eeb8321f53e","tid":1763556,"uid":91957,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:18:42.000Z","msg":"Dan Brown - 失落的符號"},{"pid":"9cd81360d8efbab61c8491a6abb544d6f2f7f03c","tid":1763556,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T07:22:40.000Z","msg":"神話+文藝復興+現代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}